  endingImage: {fileID: 21300000, guid: bb1a2f40c1ce2c543b1f8116b6c72ff3, type: 3}
  endingTitle: 'Happy Ending: World Peace'
  endingText: "Peace holds between the two worlds, and cooperation settles in.  At
    shared stations, people line up together, trading what they\u2019ve brought.
    Somewhere in the crowd, the two leaders move side by side \u2014 newly married,
    still adjusting, arguing over nothing and laughing a moment later \u2014 and
    no one seems to mind.\n\nYou\u2019re officially named Chief Honorary Translator
    of Two Worlds, complete with medals, ceremonies, and a frankly ridiculous number
    of perks. You don\u2019t translate personally anymore \u2014 just open your door
    and there they are, a whole crowd from both planets, mumbling, gesturing, crowding
    in and elbowing for a chance to be your student."
  endingBgm: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 361ff4c989cc3574db19445445e2bcc3, type: 3}
